statements.sql:
SELECT B.blotter_id, B.blotter_code, B.blotter_subject_id, B.incident_date, B.incident_area, B.complaint_name, B.complaint_date, B.complaint_statement, B.resolution, B.status, BS.blotter_subject_id, BS.blotter_name, R.resident_id, R.lastname, R.middlename, R.firstname
FROM `t_blotter` AS B
INNER JOIN r_blotter_subjects AS BS
ON B.blotter_subject_id = BS.blotter_subject_id
LEFT JOIN t_resident_basic_info AS R
ON B.accused_resident = R.resident_id
